Class AddButtonVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.AbstractContexed
      • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.html.AddButtonVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contexed, WebFormResultVisitor, FormResultVisitor

    public class AddButtonVisitor
extends AbstractContexed
implements WebFormResultVisitor
    FormResultVisitor that generates a single html button form for the target result. Note that this is used to implement the equivalent operation in the ContentBuilder interface so I can't just call the appropriate method
